item.title: 【Albums (lossy)】M4A - 1989 (Taylor's Version) in iTunes M4A format
item.description:
Can someone give me the link of 1989 (Taylor's Version) [Deluxe] the updated master on November 6 in iTunes M4A format? They say the original album's master is defective due to buzz/electronic noise, it was replaced with a digital version, although not completely fixed, and the new version is now available. Thank you in advance! ✨

Photo credits: BradH13
